3. Project description:
   - Console chat application using TCP socket.
   - Supports login, list users, 1-1 chat, logout.
4. Implementation details:
   - Python 3, socket, threading
5. Instructions to run:
   - Run `server.py`
   - Run `client.py`
   - Use commands: /login, /list, /msg, /exit
